{
  "video_id": "a6Qvzp516gY",
  "title": "How my dad's dementia changed my idea of death (and life) | Beth Malone",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 14440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been doing some thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16239.0,
      "end_time": 18000.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to kill my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19200.0,
      "end_time": 20416.0,
      "text": "I called my sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20440.0,
      "end_time": 21936.0,
      "text": "\"Listen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21960.0,
      "end_time": 23520.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been doing some thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 26320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to kill Dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27480.0,
      "end_time": 29120.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to take him to Oregon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30800.0,
      "end_time": 31976.0,
      "text": "find some heroin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32000.0,
      "end_time": 33240.0,
      "text": "and give it to him.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34720.0,
      "end_time": 36856.0,
      "text": "My dad has frontotemporal lobe dementia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36880.0,
      "end_time": 38616.0,
      "text": "or FTD."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38640.0,
      "end_time": 41576.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a confusing disease that hits people in their 50s or 60s."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41600.0,
      "end_time": 44496.0,
      "text": "It can completely change someone&#39;s personality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44520.0,
      "end_time": 46600.0,
      "text": "making them paranoid and even violent."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47400.0,
      "end_time": 49336.0,
      "text": "My dad&#39;s been sick for a decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49360.0,
      "end_time": 51896.0,
      "text": "but three years ago he got really sick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51920.0,
      "end_time": 54256.0,
      "text": "and we had to move him out of his house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54280.0,
      "end_time": 56216.0,
      "text": "the house that I grew up in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56240.0,
      "end_time": 58240.0,
      "text": "the house that he built with his own hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59160.0,
      "end_time": 64375.0,
      "text": "My strapping, cool dad with the falsetto singing voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64400.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66829.0,
      "text": "had to move into a facility for round-the-clock care"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66853.0,
      "end_time": 68333.0,
      "text": "when he was just 65."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70960.0,
      "end_time": 73616.0,
      "text": "At first my mom and sisters and I made the mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73640.0,
      "end_time": 75720.0,
      "text": "of putting him in a regular nursing home."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76599.0,
      "end_time": 77856.0,
      "text": "It was really pretty;"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77880.0,
      "end_time": 80816.0,
      "text": "it had plush carpet and afternoon art classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80840.0,
      "end_time": 82640.0,
      "text": "and a dog named Diane."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83520.0,
      "end_time": 84880.0,
      "text": "But then I got a phone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 86520.0,
      "end_time": 89640.0,
      "text": "\"Ms. Malone, we&#39;ve arrested your father.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90800.0,
      "end_time": 92000.0,
      "text": "\"What?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92760.0,
      "end_time": 95760.0,
      "text": "\"Well, he threatened everybody with cutlery."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 96960.0,
      "end_time": 99950.0,
      "text": "And then he yanked the curtains off the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 99120.0,
      "end_time": 101440.0,
      "text": "and then he tried to throw plants out the window."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102280.0,
      "end_time": 106480.0,
      "text": "And then, well, he pulled all the old ladies out of their wheelchairs.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109200.0,
      "end_time": 110576.0,
      "text": "\"All the old ladies?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110600.0,
      "end_time": 111776.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111800.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "\"What a cowboy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 114736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114760.0,
      "end_time": 116376.0,
      "text": "After he got kicked out of there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116400.0,
      "end_time": 118976.0,
      "text": "we bounced him between a bunch of state-run facilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119000.0,
      "end_time": 123256.0,
      "text": "before finding a treatment center specifically for people with dementia."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123280.0,
      "end_time": 125336.0,
      "text": "At first, he kind of liked it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125360.0,
      "end_time": 127295.0,
      "text": "but over time his health declined,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127320.0,
      "end_time": 128576.0,
      "text": "and one day I walked in"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128600.0,
      "end_time": 132816.0,
      "text": "and found him sitting hunched over on the ground wearing a onesie --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 132840.0,
      "end_time": 135000.0,
      "text": "those kinds of outfits that zip in the back."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137760.0,
      "end_time": 140976.0,
      "text": "I watched him for about an hour as he yanked at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141000.0,
      "end_time": 143400.0,
      "text": "trying to find a way out of this thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 146856.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s supposed to be practical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146880.0,
      "end_time": 149400.0,
      "text": "but to me it looked like a straightjacket."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149760.0,
      "end_time": 151280.0,
      "text": "And so I ran out."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152520.0,
      "end_time": 154800.0,
      "text": "I left him there."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 155440.0,
      "end_time": 157696.0,
      "text": "I sat in my truck -- his old truck --"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 157720.0,
      "end_time": 159336.0,
      "text": "hunched over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 159360.0,
      "end_time": 162560.0,
      "text": "this really deep guttural cry coming out of the pit of my belly."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 163480.0,
      "end_time": 166359.0,
      "text": "I just couldn&#39;t believe that my father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 167880.0,
      "end_time": 169799.0,
      "text": "the Adonis of my youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170960.0,
      "end_time": 172720.0,
      "text": "my really dear friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 173640.0,
      "end_time": 176559.0,
      "text": "would think that this kind of life was worth living anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178520.0,
      "end_time": 181280.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re programmed to prioritize productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182720.0,
      "end_time": 186560.0,
      "text": "So when a person -- an Adonis in this case --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186800.0,
      "end_time": 189736.0,
      "text": "is no longer productive in the way we expect him to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189760.0,
      "end_time": 191600.0,
      "text": "the way that he expects himself to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192600.0,
      "end_time": 194960.0,
      "text": "what value does that life have left?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195640.0,
      "end_time": 197495.0,
      "text": "That day in the truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 197520.0,
      "end_time": 201696.0,
      "text": "all I could imagine was that my dad was being tortured"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 201720.0,
      "end_time": 204680.0,
      "text": "and his body was the vessel of that torture."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206400.0,
      "end_time": 207840.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got to get him out of that body."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208600.0,
      "end_time": 211440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got to get him out of that body; I&#39;m going to kill Dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 212600.0,
      "end_time": 213840.0,
      "text": "I call my sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215400.0,
      "end_time": 217200.0,
      "text": "\"Beth,\" she said."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220800.0,
      "end_time": 222936.0,
      "text": "\"You don&#39;t want to live the rest of your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222960.0,
      "end_time": 224776.0,
      "text": "knowing that you killed your father."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224800.0,
      "end_time": 226896.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;d be arrested I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226920.0,
      "end_time": 228495.0,
      "text": "because he can&#39;t condone it."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228520.0,
      "end_time": 230776.0,
      "text": "And you don&#39;t even know how to buy heroin.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230800.0,
      "end_time": 231816.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231840.0,
      "end_time": 233960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s true, I don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 233120.0,
      "end_time": 234480.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 236200.0,
      "end_time": 238256.0,
      "text": "The truth is we talk about his death a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238280.0,
      "end_time": 240280.0,
      "text": "When will it happen? What will it be like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 240304.0,
      "end_time": 244376.0,
      "text": "But I wish that we would have talked about death when we were all healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244400.0,
      "end_time": 246880.0,
      "text": "What does my best death look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247880.0,
      "end_time": 249960.0,
      "text": "What does your best death look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250840.0,
      "end_time": 252840.0,
      "text": "But my family didn&#39;t know to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253680.0,
      "end_time": 255200.0,
      "text": "And my sister was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 255800.0,
      "end_time": 257760.0,
      "text": "I shouldn&#39;t murder Dad with heroin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258800.0,
      "end_time": 260760.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ve got to get him out of that body."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262560.0,
      "end_time": 263920.0,
      "text": "So I went to a psychic."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264760.0,
      "end_time": 266856.0,
      "text": "And then a priest, and then a support group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 266880.0,
      "end_time": 268495.0,
      "text": "and they all said the same thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 268519.0,
      "end_time": 271616.0,
      "text": "sometimes people hang on when they&#39;re worried about loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271640.0,
      "end_time": 274840.0,
      "text": "Just tell them you&#39;re safe, and it&#39;s OK to go when you&#39;re ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275600.0,
      "end_time": 276840.0,
      "text": "So I went to see Dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277840.0,
      "end_time": 280335.0,
      "text": "I found him hunched over on the ground in the onesie."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 280360.0,
      "end_time": 283376.0,
      "text": "He was staring past me and just kind of looking at the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 283400.0,
      "end_time": 284655.0,
      "text": "I gave him a ginger ale"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 284680.0,
      "end_time": 287296.0,
      "text": "and just started talking about nothing in particular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287320.0,
      "end_time": 291240.0,
      "text": "but as I was talking, he sneezed from the ginger ale."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 292000.0,
      "end_time": 295616.0,
      "text": "And the sneeze -- it jerked his body upright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295640.0,
      "end_time": 297575.0,
      "text": "sparking him back to life a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 297600.0,
      "end_time": 302776.0,
      "text": "And he just kept drinking and sneezing and sparking, over and over and over again"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302800.0,
      "end_time": 304360.0,
      "text": "until it stopped."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 305280.0,
      "end_time": 306479.0,
      "text": "And I heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 307440.0,
      "end_time": 309296.0,
      "text": "\"Heheheheheh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 309320.0,
      "end_time": 312560.0,
      "text": "heheheheheh ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 312800.0,
      "end_time": 314760.0,
      "text": "this is so fabulous."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 315760.0,
      "end_time": 317920.0,
      "text": "This is so fabulous.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 318480.0,
      "end_time": 321296.0,
      "text": "His eyes were open and he was looking at me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 321320.0,
      "end_time": 323176.0,
      "text": "and I said, \"Hi, Dad!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 323200.0,
      "end_time": 326180.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"Hiya, Beth.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 327480.0,
      "end_time": 329456.0,
      "text": "And I opened my mouth to tell him, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329480.0,
      "end_time": 332560.0,
      "text": "\"Dad, if you want to die, you can die."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 332800.0,
      "end_time": 333320.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all OK.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 333960.0,
      "end_time": 335775.0,
      "text": "But as I opened my mouth to tell him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 335800.0,
      "end_time": 337240.0,
      "text": "all I could say was, \"Dad!"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 340160.0,
      "end_time": 341600.0,
      "text": "I miss you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 342160.0,
      "end_time": 344896.0,
      "text": "And then he said, \"Well, I miss you, too.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 344920.0,
      "end_time": 347616.0,
      "text": "And then I just fell over because I&#39;m just a mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 347640.0,
      "end_time": 350880.0,
      "text": "So I fell over and I sat there with him"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 352680.0,
      "end_time": 355640.0,
      "text": "because for the first time in a long time he seemed kind of OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 356840.0,
      "end_time": 359496.0,
      "text": "And I memorized his hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 359520.0,
      "end_time": 364000.0,
      "text": "feeling so grateful that his spirit was still attached to his body."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 365400.0,
      "end_time": 367320.0,
      "text": "And in that moment I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 368120.0,
      "end_time": 370240.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not responsible for this person."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 371560.0,
      "end_time": 373560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not his doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 373800.0,
      "end_time": 374359.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not his mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 375160.0,
      "end_time": 377496.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m certainly not his God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 377520.0,
      "end_time": 381256.0,
      "text": "and maybe the best way to help him and me"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 381280.0,
      "end_time": 384800.0,
      "text": "is to resume our roles as father and daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 385360.0,
      "end_time": 386720.0,
      "text": "And so we just sat there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 387440.0,
      "end_time": 390160.0,
      "text": "calm and quiet like we&#39;ve always done."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 390400.0,
      "end_time": 391440.0,
      "text": "Nobody was productive."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 392800.0,
      "end_time": 394320.0,
      "text": "Both of us are still strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 397240.0,
      "end_time": 400296.0,
      "text": "\"OK, Dad. I&#39;m going to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 400320.0,
